Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
  courses.Schedule

public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a Schedule. Schedules are immutable.

Invariants: none

Method Detail

hasSection

public boolean hasSection(Course the_course)
Determines whether there is a Section of the_course on this Schedule. Details such as the days the Section meets or who teaches the Section are ignored.

Preconditions:
  • the_course is not null
Postconditions:
  • no Section of the_course is on this Schedule if false is returned

Parameters:
the_course - The Course being sought
Returns:
whether the_course is on this Schedule

hasSection

public boolean hasSection(Course the_course,
                          java.util.Collection<Day> the_days,
                          java.util.Collection<GeneralTime> the_times)
                   throws java.lang.NullPointerException
Determines whether this Schedule has a Section meeting the given parameters. Returns true if there exists a Section on the Schedule which is of the_course, AND only meets on days included in the_days, AND meets at one of the_times. Returns false otherwise.

Preconditions:
  • the_course != null
  • the_days is not null and does not contain null
  • the_times is not null and does not contain null
Postconditions:
  • does not return null

Parameters:
the_course - the Course being looked for
the_days - the days that the desired course may be held on
the_times - the times at which the course is desired to be held
Returns:
whether this Schedule has at least one Section meeting the given parameters.
Throws:
java.lang.NullPointerException - if the_course, the_days, or the_times are null.

getSectionsTaughtBy

public java.util.Collection<Section> getSectionsTaughtBy(User the_instructor)
Returns all the Sections taught by the given instructor.

Preconditions:
  • the_instructor is not null
  • the_instructor is an instructor
Postconditions:
  • there is no Section in the Schedule which is taught by the_instructor and also not returned

Parameters:
the_instructor - a User who is an instructor.
Returns:
all the Sections taught by the_instructor.
